trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of properties and values that are associated with an object in the <xref href="System.Printing"></xref> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de propriedades e valores que estão associados um objeto de <xref href="System.Printing"> </xref> espaço de nomes.

trans-unit.source: The collection takes the form of a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> dictionary.
trans-unit.target: A coleção assume a forma de um <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>dicionário.</xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> property of each <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> in the collection is an instance of a class that is derived from <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A>propriedade de cada <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>na coleção é uma instância de uma classe que deriva de <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref> class and provides it with the specified <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> and <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref> classe e fornece-lhe especificado <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> e <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: The data that is required to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: Os dados que é necessário para serializar ou anular a serialização de um objeto.

trans-unit.source: The context of the serialized stream, including the source and the destination.
trans-unit.target: O contexto da sequência serializada, incluindo a origem e destino.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified object (of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>) into the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o objeto especificado (uma classe que deriva de <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>) no dicionário.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A> property of `attributeValue` becomes the <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A> property of the new <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A>propriedade `attributeValue` torna-se a <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A>propriedade da nova <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty> as a whole becomes the <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> property of the new <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>Como um todo torna-se a <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A>propriedade da nova <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>

trans-unit.source: For another way to add an entry to the dictionary, see <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Para outra forma adicionar uma entrada de dicionário, consulte <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: An object (of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>) that represents a property of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto (uma classe que deriva de <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>) que representa uma propriedade de um componente de hardware ou software de sistema impressão.

trans-unit.source: Releases all the resources that are being used by the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Versões de todos os recursos que estão a ser utilizados os <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: É possível chamar Dispose quando tiver terminado de utilizando <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O método de Dispose deixa o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>num Estado não utilizável.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar Dispose, tem de libertar todas as referências para o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>para que o recoletor de lixo pode reclame a memória que a <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>foi occupying.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [recursos não geridos limpeza](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método eliminar](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada eliminar antes de libertar a última referência <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources that it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method of the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> object.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está a utilizar não irão ser libertados até que as chamadas de recoletor de lixo a <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>método o <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>objeto.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> </xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are being used by the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Liberta os recursos não geridos que estão a ser utilizados os <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref> e opcionalmente liberta os recursos geridos.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Este método é denominado pelo público <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>método e o <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>método.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> invokes the protected Dispose method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>Invoca o método de Dispose protegido com o parâmetro booleano sem nome definido como `true`.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes Dispose with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>invoca Dispose com o parâmetro definido como `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all the resources that are held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando é o parâmetro booleano `true`, este método liberta os recursos que são detidos por quaisquer objetos geridos que este <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>referências.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Este método invoca o `Dispose()` método de cada objeto referenciado.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: A adicionar.

trans-unit.source: Populates a <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> with the data that is needed to serialize the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Preenche um <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> com os dados que é necessário para serializar o <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Stores all the data that is used to serialize the object.
trans-unit.target: Armazena todos os dados que são utilizados para serializar o objeto.

trans-unit.source: Describes the context of the serialized stream, including the source and the destination.
trans-unit.target: Descreve o contexto da sequência serializada, incluindo a origem e destino.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object (of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>) that represents the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o objeto (uma classe que deriva de <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>) que representa a propriedade especificada.

trans-unit.source: The `attribName` must be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: O `attribName` tem de ser escrito exatamente o mesmo que o nome de algumas propriedade específica de um objeto de sistema de impressão, incluindo as maiúsculas e minúsculas.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueuePort", not "PrintPort", "Port", or "Queueport".
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objeto tem de ser escrito "QueuePort", não "PrintPort", "Porta" ou "Queueport".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that is represented by the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade que é representado pelo <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An object of a class that is derived from the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de uma classe que deriva de <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Implements the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable"></xref> interface and raises the deserialization event when the deserialization is complete.
trans-unit.target: Implementa o <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable"> </xref> interface e desencadeia o evento de anulação da serialização depois de concluída a anulação da serialização.

trans-unit.source: The source of the event.
trans-unit.target: A origem do evento.

trans-unit.source: Sets the value of the specified attribute to an object of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Define o valor do atributo especificado para um objeto de uma classe que deriva de <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the dictionary does not already contain `attribName`, `attribName` will be added and set to `attribValue`, provided that `attribName` is identical to `attribValue`.Name.
trans-unit.target: Se o dicionário não contém ainda `attribName`, `attribName` serão adicionados e definido como `attribValue`, desde que `attribName` é idêntico ao `attribValue`. Nome.

trans-unit.source: If these values are not identical, this method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Se estes valores não são idênticos, este método não produz qualquer efeito.

trans-unit.source: The name of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: O nome do atributo.

trans-unit.source: An object of a type that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de um tipo que deriva de <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: attribName is already in the dictionary and it already has the value attribValue.
trans-unit.target: attribNamejá se encontra no dicionário e já tem o valor attribValue.
